extends ./templates/layouts/page

block main
  main
    h1.Page-title Rob Wierzbowski

    .Page-content
      p I'm a design-minded developer focusing on modern front-end development, process, and teamwork. I love the good parts of JavaScript, automating everything, and actually think CSS is awesome.

      p You'll usually find me living and working in Pittsburgh, PA.

    .Page-cta
